      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNNY BLUE (8) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Was fourth last time (20.35) over 340m at this track in a Grade 5. Solid record here at this trip including six wins. Can make amends. OCCULENT (4) produced a moderate effort last time when seventh at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Canya Handle It (30.23) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Should play a prominent role. DAM PANAMA (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (20.30) in a Grade 5 at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. MERGER (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
